  "description_text": "Nidek Nuvo 10 Liter Oxygen Concentrator\n\nNidek Nuvo 10 litre is a well-established American oxygen concentrator in the Indian market that supplies oxygen at the flow rate of 2-10 LPM at oxygen purity of 87-95% at all flow levels. \n\nWeight: Nidek Nuvo 10 litres weighs 29.26 kg.\n\nSound: The machine emits sound at 58 dB. \n\nOperating Altitude: The operating altitude of Nidek Nuvo 10 LPM is 5000 feet.\n\nOutlet Pressure: The machine gives outlet pressure at 15 psi.\n\nPower Consumption: Nidek Nuvo 10 LPM uses 600 watts of power.\n\nFlow Meter: The device comes with ball type flow meter which can be set between 2-10 LPM.\n\nAlarms: Loss of power, system malfunction\n\nCertifications and Approvals: Nidek Nuvo 10 LPM is CE certified and FDA approved.\n\nWarranty: This machine has a warranty period of 1 year.\n\nWhat's in the Box?\n\n\n\tNuvo 10 oxygen concentrator\n\tHumidifier Bottle\n\tNasal cannula\n\tUser Manual",
